<h3>在Lion安装rails</h3>

<pre><code>gem install rails
</code></pre>

<h3>创建rails的应用</h3>

<pre><code>rails new myapp
</code></pre>

<h3>启动应用</h3>

<pre><code>cd myapp
rails server
</code></pre>

<h3>进入</h3>

<pre><code>http://localhost:3000
"Welcome aboard: You're riding Ruby on Rails!"
</code></pre>
